---
profile: moderate

## Org default: keep this file generic.
## Repo-specific exclude paths should be added in repo-local overrides, not here.

## Rules moved to warn rather than fail — review these over time and promote to errors
warn_list:
  - no-changed-when           ## shell/command tasks ideally have changed_when; warn for now
  - experimental              ## experimental rules may have false positives

exclude_paths:
  - .git/
  - .dev-venv/
  - .venv/
